Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.02,0:00:10.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久违了 猪鹿蝶小鬼…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.07,0:00:13.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…是角都吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.59,0:00:15.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金已经被干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.95,0:00:19.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个角我们也非常了解
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.54,0:00:23.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来就到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.59,0:00:25.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使用影子的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.01,0:00:30.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在这里就说明飞段被打败了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.56,0:00:35.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是在祈祷中被砍头了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.36,0:00:41.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他没出现在这里说明还没死
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.64,0:00:43.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道他什么时候能烂掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.46,0:00:49.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有飞车 失了金银 只能防守了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.43,0:00:55.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来就有五个了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.23,0:01:00.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来 那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.97,0:01:03.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有五个心脏…那得打倒五回才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.61,0:01:05.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.53,0:01:09.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 也该角出击了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.62,0:01:23.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.04,0:01:27.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我也缴了你们的金银
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.95,0:01:31.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是谁呢 你们不想知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.52,0:01:35.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加藤断
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.96,0:01:38.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纲手公主的相好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.35,0:01:40.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.85,0:01:50.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猿飞阿斯玛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.33,0:01:54.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三代火影之子 你们的师父
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.86,0:01:56.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯玛老师
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.65,0:02:02.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来会吃棋子的不只是你们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.64,0:02:04.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我手上还有好几个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.05,0:02:07.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是讽刺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.31,0:02:10.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.15,0:02:13.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丁座
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.32,0:02:16.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四紫炎阵还没准备好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.96,0:02:19.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快把我封进结界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.68,0:02:21.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我使出灵化术之前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.40,0:02:26.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没那么简单 对手可是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.11,0:02:32.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像有什么黑色的不明物体出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.84,0:02:33.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.75,0:02:39.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反击开始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.57,0:02:47.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们之间还有账没算清呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.66,0:02:49.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直记着呢 羊栖菜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.08,0:02:51.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.04,0:02:53.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可记不住廉价的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.94,0:02:56.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说有钱能使鬼推磨…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.04,0:02:59.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死过一次的你不妨告诉我们是否属实吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.15,0:03:04.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.27,0:03:05.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出云先生 子铁先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.33,0:03:07.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹿丸 丁次 井野
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.39,0:03:10.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们合力封印这个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.74,0:03:11.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.62,0:03:16.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出云 子铁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.25,0:03:18.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,角都交给你们和懒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.24,0:03:20.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙擅长土遁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.16,0:03:23.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以懒为核心用雷遁来战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.89,0:03:25.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹿丸 你们去解决阿斯玛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.40,0:03:29.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是这样也太…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.28,0:03:32.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯玛前辈是他们的师父啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.59,0:03:33.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此残酷…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.25,0:03:37.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是阿斯玛的部下 原第十班
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.42,0:03:40.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比任何人都熟悉阿斯玛的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.64,0:03:42.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以胜算最高
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.79,0:03:43.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.23,0:03:46.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们别说丧气话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.42,0:03:49.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是战争 一定要赢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.35,0:03:51.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.62,0:03:54.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.71,0:05:52.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.39,0:05:55.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 丁次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.80,0:05:58.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下成了我和鹿丸在单挑了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.76,0:06:01.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…很疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.67,0:06:03.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我力量很大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.62,0:06:06.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想弄疼你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.27,0:06:08.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这是瞧不起人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.29,0:06:12.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来试试弄疼我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.70,0:06:13.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来啊来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.51,0:06:14.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哭吧 叫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.82,0:06:16.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 我很疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.79,0:06:20.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 真麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.48,0:06:21.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丁次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.89,0:06:24.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这份温柔是在关心同伴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.11,0:06:26.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯玛老师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.76,0:06:29.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可是大错特错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.77,0:06:35.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和更强的对手练习只会变得更加强大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.62,0:06:39.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没感觉到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.44,0:06:42.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就让你们切身体会一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.39,0:06:46.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在开始和我对战
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.89,0:06:49.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要打中我一拳 就算合格
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.18,0:06:54.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 一小时之内不能成功的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.65,0:06:56.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丁次 不单单是你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.10,0:07:00.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,井野 鹿丸 你们三个一起回学校
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.64,0:07:03.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.75,0:07:07.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了他们 把我当成敌人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.42,0:07:11.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将你的温柔转变成力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.56,0:07:14.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丁次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.97,0:07:17.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.65,0:07:21.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.29,0:07:23.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点去阿斯玛那边
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.13,0:07:29.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果真的珍惜同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.25,0:07:36.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就该考虑如何变得更强 而不是逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.74,0:07:39.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这才是真正的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.25,0:07:40.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这胆小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.62,0:07:46.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了 鹿丸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.04,0:07:51.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.52,0:07:52.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹿丸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.23,0:07:57.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,井野 你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.46,0:08:01.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丁次 好好看看周围的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.74,0:08:29.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放马过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.85,0:08:36.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丁座先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.23,0:08:38.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.15,0:08:59.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丁次 还记得阿斯玛老师的遗言吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.55,0:09:05.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丁次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.54,0:09:09.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是个会替伙伴着想的温柔男人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.67,0:09:11.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.81,0:09:15.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才能成为比别人更强的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.96,0:09:19.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要对自己更有自信
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.07,0:09:38.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你虽逞强好胜 却是个会照顾人的好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.44,0:09:41.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丁次和鹿丸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.14,0:09:44.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们都很粗心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.48,0:09:46.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.13,0:09:54.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧 你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.11,0:10:02.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.84,0:10:13.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.53,0:10:20.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苦无只是为了分散我的注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.81,0:10:22.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这才是真正的目的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.95,0:10:31.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.65,0:10:39.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.61,0:10:43.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯玛先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.99,0:10:45.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来阻止你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.32,0:10:49.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然是临时组合 但配合得不错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.42,0:10:51.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保持下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.54,0:10:53.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.77,0:10:56.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目的不是破坏而是抓捕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.54,0:10:57.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.20,0:11:00.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,封印班的家伙在搞什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.74,0:11:08.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.76,0:11:09.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.33,0:11:21.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火遁.灰积烧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.64,0:11:24.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.59,0:11:25.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,障眼法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.49,0:12:00.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.49,0:12:24.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了找重要的刀浪费了不少时间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.88,0:12:27.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来…那个角都呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.76,0:12:35.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才捡到的这个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.79,0:12:45.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然很管用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.91,0:12:50.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.78,0:13:00.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用雷的家伙干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.40,0:13:04.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是个不错的玩意 谁掉的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.82,0:13:12.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉非常消耗查克拉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.06,0:13:15.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在可没空管这些
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.96,0:13:26.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们以为我会坐以待毙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.66,0:13:29.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,懒队长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.46,0:13:32.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总部的指示我收到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.05,0:13:33.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.58,0:13:41.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.90,0:13:43.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才应该用雷遁一口气…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.87,0:13:44.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.17,0:13:48.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前的战斗飙过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.55,0:13:49.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑斑差
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.65,0:13:54.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,励挫锁苛素
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.93,0:13:57.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,双重黑斑差
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.06,0:14:01.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查克拉不太够了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.56,0:14:03.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.10,0:14:05.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追吧 子铁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.18,0:14:10.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.87,0:14:26.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已经有所觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.49,0:14:29.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以也请老师做好准备
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.41,0:14:34.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丁次 鹿丸 井野
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.81,0:14:38.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们成长了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.49,0:14:49.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托您的福…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.33,0:14:54.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我见识一下吧 猪鹿蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.73,0:15:02.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一口气缩短距离
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.14,0:15:06.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,替身术
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.55,0:15:07.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.38,0:15:13.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的动作太迟钝了 丁次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.20,0:15:15.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作一点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.60,0:15:16.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.92,0:15:19.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹿丸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.86,0:15:23.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用影子模仿术张网 把我引向丁次的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.42,0:15:24.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早有这个打算
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.41,0:15:26.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影子模仿术
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.50,0:15:28.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有一招
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.73,0:15:31.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他发现是心转身之术
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.27,0:15:34.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是虚招 也会躲开的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.26,0:15:36.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果避开影子模仿术
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.20,0:15:37.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会进入井野的死角
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.69,0:15:38.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我想得一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.88,0:15:39.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后是那里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.91,0:15:41.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部分倍化之术
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.14,0:15:44.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将军了 阿斯玛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.89,0:15:46.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是现在 丁次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.53,0:15:47.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.95,0:15:51.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在干什么 丁次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.58,0:15:54.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作点 不是有所觉悟了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.90,0:15:55.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丁次…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.56,0:15:57.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.36,0:16:00.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我果然做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.42,0:16:03.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没办法打老师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.71,0:16:04.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丁次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.32,0:16:06.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,躲开
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.26,0:16:07.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.07,0:16:10.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风遁.风尘之术
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.15,0:16:13.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 被躲开了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.78,0:16:23.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.00,0:16:25.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.20,0:16:27.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.87,0:16:30.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.76,0:16:32.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不是丧气的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.70,0:16:35.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不是已经有阻止阿斯玛的觉悟了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.97,0:16:37.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这算什么 丁次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.25,0:16:40.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我只是你的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.21,0:16:41.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个已死之人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.89,0:16:42.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毋须手下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.07,0:16:45.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.98,0:16:47.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.69,0:16:51.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那个时候 老师也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.81,0:16:59.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 丁次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.34,0:17:02.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去 你们三个想一起回学校吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.56,0:17:09.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.96,0:17:15.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丁次 战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.76,0:17:17.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个胆小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.02,0:17:25.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 反而起反效果了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.52,0:17:28.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丁次不是因害怕而不敢出手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.02,0:17:33.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是不想让阿斯玛老师尝到自己所受的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.04,0:17:37.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就是个彻底温柔的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.52,0:17:40.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 这样下去的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.62,0:17:43.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.46,0:17:45.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丁次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.00,0:17:47.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,适可而止吧 你这个肥猪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.67,0:17:54.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹿丸 你刚才说肥猪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.89,0:17:58.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说了 肥猪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.89,0:18:00.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是阿斯玛老师说的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.79,0:18:05.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗 阿斯玛老师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.18,0:18:09.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.48,0:18:13.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说“那肥猪的拳头一发都不会打中”
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.92,0:18:15.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说过头了吧 井野
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.43,0:18:19.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是老师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.44,0:18:23.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫我肥猪的家伙也不可饶恕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.86,0:18:34.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.48,0:18:40.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我果然无法对老师下手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.84,0:18:45.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.62,0:18:48.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我一个人回学校就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.43,0:18:51.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放过鹿丸和井野吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.48,0:19:01.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丁次 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.11,0:19:03.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我输了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.35,0:19:10.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便愤怒透顶 你也能控制自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.45,0:19:12.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为对方考虑 这是真正的温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.29,0:19:15.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将这份温柔保持下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.52,0:19:19.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这份温柔早晚会有转化成力量的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.81,0:19:23.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是 对战时…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.82,0:19:25.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个没事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.46,0:19:27.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我不喜欢和阿斯玛老师 鹿丸 井野
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.78,0:19:30.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及村里的大伙动手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.29,0:19:33.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是在面对企图伤害大伙的敌人时
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.90,0:19:35.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会战斗的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.06,0:19:43.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕鹿丸和井野以后一直叫我肥猪…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.09,0:19:50.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 鹿丸 井野
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.02,0:19:52.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丁次不是肥猪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.01,0:19:55.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是有些丰满
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.48,0:20:10.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯玛老师不是让我保持那份温柔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.67,0:20:14.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是现在 丁次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.59,0:20:17.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的温柔我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.29,0:20:21.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但此刻打倒我才是温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.19,0:20:25.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在正是将你的温柔转化为力量的时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.27,0:20:27.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是现在 丁次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.55,0:20:30.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了 阻止我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.20,0:20:38.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,适可而止吧 肥猪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.16,0:20:39.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来打我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.09,0:20:43.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肥猪…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.14,0:20:48.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才你说肥猪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.15,0:20:53.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.14,0:20:56.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是肥猪…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.00,0:21:03.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是有些丰满
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.68,0:22:40.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本以为起誓只是个仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.89,0:22:47.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原以为长大成人自然而然身心都会坚强起来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.98,0:22:53.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 但是我现在必须要改变
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.65,0:22:55.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集「火影忍者 疾风传」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.96,0:22:57.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「完美的猪鹿蝶」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.51,0:23:01.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在要从蛹生蝶 飞翔吧
